name: THE SEA X
description:
THE SEA X was a writing performance I did last year at the festival of teatrouaifai.com
It was a Google drive archive so the audience watched, edited, and wrote it with me. 
My inspiration was Patriarchal Poetry from Gertrude Stein and the webcamgirls world. I tried to answer what could be patriarchal poetry today for me as the virtual performer I became.
